    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":16,"isDeleted":false,"id":"text-msgs","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":772,"y":350,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":236,"height":250,"seed":16,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":15,"fontFamily":1,"text":"Server messages\n\ninit\n  initial view snapshot\nsync (every ~30s)\n  REPLACE state, not merge\nnew-token\n  delta event\nupdate-token\n  price/holders refresh\nremove-token\n  fell out of view\n\nKeep-alive: {event:'ping'}","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Server messages","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":17,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-talk","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":40,"y":680,"strokeColor":"#5f3dc4","backgroundColor":"#d0bfff","width":980,"height":300,"seed":17,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":18,"isDeleted":false,"id":"text-talk-title","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":56,"y":690,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":900,"height":32,"seed":18,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":22,"fontFamily":1,"text":"📹 Video talking points","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"📹 Video talking points","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":19,"isDeleted":false,"id":"text-talk-body","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":56,"y":730,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":960,"height":240,"seed":19,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"text":"1. The problem — sniping fresh tokens means racing bots; you need data BEFORE indexers like DexScreener catch up.\n2. Why Pulse Stream V2 — one WebSocket, every chain, every DEX (pump.fun, Moonshot, Raydium, Uniswap). Server-side filtering on age, liquidity, holdings, taxes.\n3. Architecture — show the 3 boxes: Mobula → pulse-sniper → Telegram. ~150 lines per module, no infra.\n4. Live demo — npm run dev, show 'pulse stream connected', then a sync hit. Open Telegram, show alert with Chart + Buy buttons.\n5. The score — explain the 0..100 logic: holders, socials, mint authority, organic trades, dev/sniper concentration. Color-coded emoji 🟢🟡🟠🔴.\n6. Resilience — auto-reconnect with exponential backoff, re-subscribe on every reconnect, SQLite dedup so the 30s sync replay doesn't double-ping.\n7. Closing — 'Built in one afternoon on top of Mobula Pulse, the same data layer used by exchanges and trading desks. Repo open-source.'\n\nKey numbers to drop: < 60s detection · 2k$ min liq · 5 DEXs · 3 chains · MIT licensed.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"1. The problem — sniping fresh tokens means racing bots; you need data BEFORE indexers like DexScreener catch up.\n2. Why Pulse Stream V2 — one WebSocket, every chain, every DEX (pump.fun, Moonshot, Raydium, Uniswap). Server-side filtering on age, liquidity, holdings, taxes.\n3. Architecture — show the 3 boxes: Mobula → pulse-sniper → Telegram. ~150 lines per module, no infra.\n4. Live demo — npm run dev, show 'pulse stream connected', then a sync hit. Open Telegram, show alert with Chart + Buy buttons.\n5. The score — explain the 0..100 logic: holders, socials, mint authority, organic trades, dev/sniper concentration. Color-coded emoji 🟢🟡🟠🔴.\n6. Resilience — auto-reconnect with exponential backoff, re-subscribe on every reconnect, SQLite dedup so the 30s sync replay doesn't double-ping.\n7. Closing — 'Built in one afternoon on top of Mobula Pulse, the same data layer used by exchanges and trading desks. Repo open-source.'\n\nKey numbers to drop: < 60s detection · 2k$ min liq · 5 DEXs · 3 chains · MIT licensed.","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25}
